	<key>PayloadDescription</key>
	<string>iMIUI is a theme for iOS 6 and above that shares aspects with Android, to have the theme be complete also install Rage3hacks Defualt App Hider.
+Created By: onehalfkiller and nqlw
+Homepage: http://onehalfkiller.com/imiui 
+Requires iOS: 6.0+
+FREE
+Auto Updating: No
+Ad Free 
This Package is hosted on the Defualt Repo 
Only install pacages from trusted/tested source.
</string>
